    "An adversarial attack is a deliberate attempt to fool a machine by inputting modified data that causes the model to make mistakes.",
    "We employ adversarial attack methods to explore the capabilities and limitations of LLMs in graduate level chemistry education.",
    "We selected as the primary AI model for this study due to its accessibility and widespread use within different contexts.",
    "ChatGPT is freely available through a user-friendly interface and its ability to generate human-like conversations makes it a suitable candidate for evaluating LLMs in educational settings.",
    "We focus on topics within general chemistry, including acids and bases, atomic structure, chemical bonds, chemical reactions and instrumental laboratory techniques."
